Nutrient data for: MILKA CHOCOLATE PIECES ALPINE MILK 1.702 KG, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622300295127

Ingredients: Sugar, cocoa butter, skimmed MILK powder, cocoa mass, whey powder (from MILK), MILK fat, HAZELNUT paste, emulsifier (SOYA lecithin), flavouring (vanillin). Cocoa solids 30% minimum.
